subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
Dating and Courtship
lead_paragraph: Ricky Stenhouse Jr., the First Boyfriend of auto racing, is leading a wave of young drivers who could transform Nascar as a generation of champions nears the end of their careers.
